data.description: Prepare to fall in love with this extraordinary property, beautifully situated in a mature, tree-lined neighborhood that exudes timeless charm and elegance. Not only does this home boast three generously sized bedrooms and two full baths in the main residence, but it also features two separate, income-generating garage apartments—each with its own bedroom and bathroom. This is an unparalleled opportunity to enjoy great living while offsetting your mortgage through rental income.
